`,a.jsxs(t.p,{children:["Patients Waiting Area Queue Management System v1.0 (sourcecodester #18348) exposes ",a.jsx(t.code,{children:"php/api_patient_schedule.php"}),", which concatenates the ",a.jsx(t.code,{children:"appointmentID"})," query parameter directly into a SQL statement. Staff registration is open via ",a.jsx(t.code,{children:"api_register_staff.php"}),", so any unauthenticated attacker can self-register, log in, and reach the vulnerable endpoint. In practice this reduces to a low barrier auth bypass into full database read."]}),`
