`,a.jsx(t.p,{children:"The vulnerability discloses every staff record, including IDs, names, emails, password hashes, role, and active status. Hashes can be cracked offline to recover credentials for higher privileged accounts than the attacker's self registered role. Read access also extends to any other table in the database, covering patients, appointments, and schedules."}),`
